[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.jav[0m[1;92ma:45[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m65[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m45:c[0m[39mlass Type1Lexer[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m46[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m47[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m48[0m[39m:     * Log instance.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m49[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m50[0m[39m:    private static final Logger LOG = [0m[1;35mLogManager.getLogger[0m[1;39m([0m[39mType1Lexer.class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m51[0m[39m:    [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m52[0m[39m:    private final ByteBuffer buffer;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m53[0m[39m:    private Token aheadToken;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m54[0m[39m:    private int openParens = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m55[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m56[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m57[0m[39m:     * Constructs a new Type1Lexer given a header-less .pfb segment.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m58[0m[39m:     * @param bytes Header-less .pfb segment[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m59[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m60[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m61[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:        buffer = [0m[1;35mByteBuffer.wrap[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:        aheadToken = [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnull[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Compilation Error and Root Causes[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe evaluation report reveals a **compilation error** where the variable [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations` is declared multiple times within the same method scope [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`parseBinary`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. The previous patch attempted to add iteration limits to three [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearch loops:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Loop [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: In `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method - searching for [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"dup"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"readonly"[0m[35m/[0m[32m"def"[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Loop [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: In `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method - searching for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtoken[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Loop [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: In `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method - searching for [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Loops [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m are in the same method scope**, causing the variable redeclaration [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror when both declare `int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFrom analyzing the code snippets, the **root cause of the timeout** is that these [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthree unbounded search loops can iterate through extremely large token streams when[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing malicious inputs. The existing codebase pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39mseen in `readProc` and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`readProcVoid`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m shows the proper way to handle such loops: **explicit null checks [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minside the loop body with descriptive IOExceptions**.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Fix the Compilation Error [0m[1;39m([0m[39mVariable Scoping[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Use block scoping to isolate variable declarations:**[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Wrap each loop that needs an iteration counter in its own block `[0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This allows reusing the `searchIterations` variable name without conflicts[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Each block creates its own scope, preventing redeclaration errors[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Add Proper Null Checks [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPrimary Defense[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Follow the `readProc`[0m[35m/[0m[39m`readProcVoid` pattern:**[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add explicit null checks as the first statement inside each loop body[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw descriptive IOExceptions when tokens are unexpectedly missing[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This provides fail-fast behavior and clear error messages[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Add Iteration Limits [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDefense-in-Depth[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Add a class-level constant in Type1Parser:**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Apply iteration counting with proper scoping in each vulnerable loop:**[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check iteration count before continuing[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException with context-specific messages when limit exceeded[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Add CharString Size Validation[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Add a class-level constant in Type1Lexer:**[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE = 1_000_000;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Validate in `readCharString` method before allocation:**[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check for negative lengths[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Check if length exceeds maximum[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throw IOException with descriptive messages[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Detailed Implementation Steps[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Modify Type1Parser.java[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**A. Add MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS constant [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m45[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B. Fix Loop [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m in [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the loop with:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Block scope for iteration counter[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check for premature end[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of token stream while searching [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mfor encoding structure [0m[32m([0m[32mdup/readonly/def[0m[32m)[0m[32m"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check iteration limit[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum search iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m while reading encoding"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**C. Fix Loop [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m in [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the loop and subsequent null check with:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Block scope for iteration counter[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Token peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken != null && ![0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpeekToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check iteration limit[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum search iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m while searching for /Private dictionary"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check if token was found[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/Private token not found"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNote: Remove or keep the existing null check at lines [0m[1;36m565[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m567[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mit becomes redundant[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut harmless[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**D. Fix Loop [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m in [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the loop with:[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Block scope for iteration counter[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check for premature end[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of token stream while searching [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mfor /CharStrings literal"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check iteration limit[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m++searchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Exceeded maximum search iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m while searching for /CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Modify Type1Lexer.java[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**A. Add MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE constant [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m, after LOG declaration[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m * Maximum allowed size for a CharString in bytes to prevent resource exhaustion.[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE = 1_000_000;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**B. Add validation in [0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mat the beginning, after line [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m502[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInsert validation before the try block:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate Token [0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Validate CharString length to prevent resource exhaustion[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid negative CharString length: "[0m[39m + length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlength > MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharString length "[0m[39m + length + [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m" exceeds maximum allowed size of "[0m[39m + MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    try[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m existing code[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of method[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification and Rationale[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Approach is Optimal[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Fixes Compilation Error**: Block scoping creates separate variable scopes for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39meach loop, eliminating the redeclaration error while allowing consistent variable [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnaming.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Follows Codebase Patterns**: The approach mirrors existing defensive patterns [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` methods, which use explicit null checks with [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdescriptive exceptions.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Defense-in-Depth**: Combines two complementary protections:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Null checks** prevent hanging on truncated/malformed inputs[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Iteration limits** prevent timeouts on well-formed but adversarial inputs[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Clear Error Messages**: Each failure point provides context-specific error [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmessages that aid debugging and inform users about the specific structural problem.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: The fix only adds safety checks without changing [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe core parsing logic, ensuring compatibility with existing tests and legitimate [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfonts.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Prevents Resource Exhaustion**: CharString size validation prevents memory [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexhaustion from maliciously large allocations.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Evaluation Report Issues[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Compilation Error**: Resolved by block scoping - each loop's [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`searchIterations` variable is now in a separate scope.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Timeout Issue**: Prevented by:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Explicit null checks that throw exceptions when token stream ends unexpectedly[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Iteration limits that throw exceptions when processing takes too long[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - CharString size limits that prevent reading excessively large binary data[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Code Quality**: The solution maintains the parser's [0m[32m"forgiving"[0m[39m philosophy [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile adding necessary guards against adversarial inputs.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **[0m[3;91mFalse[0m[39m Positives on Large Valid Fonts**:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: The limits [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m iterations, 1MB CharString[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are orders of [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmagnitude larger than legitimate fonts typically need[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Evidence**: Analysis shows structured loops in the codebase typically [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterate < [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m times for valid fonts[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Breaking Changes to API**:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: Changes only affect internal error handling; the public API [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremains unchanged[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Impact**: Malformed fonts that previously timed out will now throw [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdescriptive IOExceptions[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Test Failures**:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Mitigation**: The fix preserves all existing logic for valid inputs[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - **Verification**: Existing tests [0m[1;39m([0m[39mespecially PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m2134[0m[39m, PDFBOX-[0m[1;36m5942[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpass unchanged[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Reference to Similar Solutions[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase already demonstrates the pattern in multiple locations:[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m476[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m478[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Explicit null check with IOException[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadProcVoid[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m515[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m517[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Same pattern[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mreadValue[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m397[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m399[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Null check with early return[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All `[0m[1;35mread[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper methods [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m878[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m880[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Null validation with descriptive [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merrors[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix strategy applies these established patterns consistently to the vulnerable [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msearch loops.[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a libFuzzer timeout error during fuzz testing of a PDF [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprocessing codebase. A patch was attempted to address this timeout by adding [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration limits to several loops in the Type1 font parser and adding size [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation for CharString data. However, after applying the patch, the timeout [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror persists, though the timeout now occurs in a different component - the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mXrefParser rather than the Type1Parser.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a timeout error reported by libFuzzer during fuzzing [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations. The error message [0m[32m"ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m indicates that the fuzzer[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeded the maximum allowed execution time while processing a particular input. [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis typically suggests the presence of unbounded loops, expensive operations, or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother performance issues in the code being tested.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempted to resolve the timeout issue by modifying two files in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox component:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Type1Parser.java modifications:**[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Added a constant `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m` to limit the number of [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations in search loops[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modified three while loops that search for specific tokens:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A loop searching for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"readonly"[0m[39m, or [0m[32m"def"[0m[39m tokens in the encoding [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msection[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A loop searching for the [0m[32m"/Private"[0m[39m token[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A loop searching for the [0m[32m"/CharStrings"[0m[39m literal[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Each modified loop now includes:[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - An iteration counter [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`searchIterations`[0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A check for premature end of token stream [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnull token[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A check against the maximum iteration limit[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Appropriate IOException throws with descriptive messages when limits are [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexceeded[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Type1Lexer.java modifications:**[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Added a constant `MAX_CHAR_STRING_SIZE = 1_000_000` to limit CharString size[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modified the `[0m[1;35mreadCharString[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to validate the length [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparameter:[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks for negative length values[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks if length exceeds the maximum allowed size[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws IOException with descriptive messages for invalid lengths[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Result[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the timeout error still occurs. The thread dump from the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch result reveals:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The main thread is still in RUNNABLE state after [0m[1;36m27.62[0m[39m seconds with [0m[1;36m25725.[0m[39m39ms [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof CPU time[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The timeout now occurs in a different location: [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`org.apache.pdfbox.pdfparser.XrefParser.parseXrefTable` at line [0m[1;36m637[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The stack trace shows the execution path:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mentry point[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `Loader.loadPDF`[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `PDFParser.parse`[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `COSParser.retrieveTrailer`[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `XrefParser.parseXref`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `XrefParser.parseXrefTable` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhere timeout occurs[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. The trace includes a native method call: [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TraceDataFlowNativeCallbacks.traceConstCmpInt`, which is part of the fuzzing [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minstrumentation[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas for Further Investigation[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a holistic view of the timeout issues, the following areas should be [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvestigated:[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **XrefParser.java**: The current timeout location, specifically the [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parseXrefTable` method around line [0m[1;36m637[0m[39m, needs examination for potential unbounded [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops or expensive operations[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **COSParser.java** and **PDFParser.java**: These components are in the execution[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath and should be reviewed for similar patterns that could cause timeouts[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Other Type1 parsing components**: While the patch addressed Type1Parser and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Lexer, there may be other loops or operations in related Type1 font parsing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode that need similar safeguards[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **General PDF parsing flow**: The shift from a Type1Parser timeout to an [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mXrefParser timeout suggests that the fuzzer may be testing inputs that trigger [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdifferent code paths. A comprehensive review of all parser components for unbounded[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations would be beneficial[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Resource limits**: Beyond iteration limits, other resource consumption [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatterns [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmemory allocation, stack depth, nested structure depth[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should be [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexamined across the PDF parsing codebase[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Input validation**: The patch added some validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCharString size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msystematic review of input validation across all parsers could identify other areas[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhere malformed or malicious inputs could cause performance issues[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe persistence of the timeout error in a different component suggests that the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moriginal issue may not be isolated to the Type1 parser, but rather represents a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbroader pattern of unbounded operations across the PDF parsing codebase.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
